{"tid":1592720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國央視旗下CGTN 英國涉偏頗報導香港遭查","createTime":"2019-09-24T17:47:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T07:20:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04d140902d82b9034c69acc41803dc51b3b020c8","tid":1592720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:47:15.000Z","msg":"中國央視旗下CGTN 英國涉偏頗報導香港遭查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190924-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8Bcgtn-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%89%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%AD%E6%9F%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20190924-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258Bcgtn-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2581%258F%25E9%25A0%2597%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B0%258E%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%259F%25A5&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=3ee0badf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20190924-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%AE%E8%A6%96%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8Bcgtn-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%89%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97%E5%A0%B1%E5%B0%8E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%81%AD%E6%9F%A5</a><br />\n<strong><br />\n中國官媒央視旗下的中國國際電視台（CGTN）屢被質疑報道偏頗。英國通訊管理局或針對CGTN 連日來都有製作不少報道，講述香港反送中運動，不過內容普遍與其他大陸官媒口徑一致有關。</strong><br />\n<br />\n據聯合早報今天報道，中國央視旗下CGTN 遭英通訊管理局調查，被指反修例報道或違規。<br />\n<br />\n該報道說，中國官媒央視旗下的中國國際電視台（CGTN）屢被質疑報道偏頗。英國通訊管理局周一宣布，將針對CGTN 展開四項新的調查，研究該電視台有關香港反修例運動的報道有否違規。<br />\n<br />\n報道引據英媒《衛報》消息，英國通訊管理局宣布，針對CGTN 在8月及9月有關香港反修例報道，展開四項調查，以研究該台有否觸犯&ldquo;公正報道&rdquo;的守則。英國通訊管理局發言人證實，是在局方內部例行監管後決定展開調查，而並非為回應公眾投訴。<br />\n<br />\n據報道說，較早前，英國通訊管理局已因為CGTN播放認罪影片，就私隱、公平性等問題展開4四項調查。加上新增的四項，CGTN 如今面臨共八項英國通訊管理局調查。<br />\nCGTN 連日來都有製作不少報道，講述香港反送中運動，不過內容普遍與其他大陸官媒口徑一致。其中一段約9分鐘的影片，形容是反對派&ldquo;煽動&rdquo;民眾，並詳述民主派人士與外國勢力的接觸，影片最後反問觀眾：&ldquo;你還認為在香港發生的是民主示威嗎？&rdquo;"},{"pid":"a5a2ebbe7312c56dcdb8414086183661655906b0","tid":1592720,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"eda17617c89845eadda5a22caf0946e9fc7d35ce","tid":1592720,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e95af20695b2cddcb75480a1b3881e518c4a3da9","tid":1592720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b64bb6a7bb7e6bb475d9d2e39c60dbec0dee04d","tid":1592720,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"唔偏頗就唔係紅媒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29056a8b13bc64cc1bf0fb0c8870dfdc6e609b1e","tid":1592720,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b64bb6a7bb7e6bb475d9d2e39c60dbec0dee04d","tid":1592720,"uid":134415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:55:24.000Z","msg":"唔偏頗就唔係紅媒喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbced96ada6e18327ccf927d9975c28e0b7aea35","tid":1592720,"uid":176112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T01:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7726edbda09a55aa858ecc7718ad2a26e0b2fd32","tid":1592720,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"佢中立，我反而仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d569bfe3fc2b1dc110979c4beb30d26cbaac63a6","tid":1592720,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:28:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417176d9dec0ca06604f44e1421f079079740ff2","tid":1592720,"uid":64636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"就要比外國知大陸點報新聞"},{"pid":"1b23eae25cb73bd6969e7cf90b68aeea631751da","tid":1592720,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}